Freesms,is,a,Nigerian,bulk,SMS,service,that,can,deliver,messages,to,more,than,countries,around,the,world,They,offer,their,services,to,businesses,organizations,and,individuals,Developers,can,integrate,the,Freesms,messaging,gateway,into,their,websites,or,perform,resale,functions,via,REST,API,From,the,messaging,gateway,users,can,send,SMS,and,check,their,account,balances